                  <em>Mythic Game Master Emulator 2nd Edition</em> and related names are trademarks of and © Word Mill Creative LLC. Used
                  under license. JHD develops the official licensed digital companions.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-license">
