                <p>
                  Subject to these Terms, JHD grants you a limited, non‑exclusive, non‑transferable, revocable license to install and use
                  the apps for personal, non‑commercial tabletop play. You may not copy, distribute, sell, sublicense, modify, reverse
                  engineer, or create derivative works except as permitted by law.
                </p>
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>Official content:</strong> Licensed Mythic text and tables are for in‑app use only; do not extract or redistribute.</li>
                  <li><strong>User content:</strong> Your journals, scenes, and custom tables remain yours and stay on your device unless you export/share them.</li>
                  <li><strong>Prohibited use:</strong> No unlawful, infringing, or automated scraping activities.</li>
                </ul>
              </section>

              <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-purchases">
                <h2 id="terms-purchases">4) Purchases, Subscriptions, and Taxes</h2>
                <p>
                  Pricing and availability may vary by platform and region. Purchases made through the Apple App Store, Google Play, or
                  itch.io are processed by those stores; their terms and tax/VAT handling apply.
