                  <li><strong>Taxes/VAT:</strong> Collected and remitted by the storefront as applicable.</li>
                  <li><strong>Receipts:</strong> Provided by the store or by itch.io for direct desktop purchases.</li>
                </ul>
              </section>

              <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-refunds">
                <h2 id="terms-refunds">5) Refunds</h2>
                <p>
                  Refunds for purchases made via a platform store are handled under that store’s policy. If you need help initiating a
                  request, contact us and we’ll point you to the correct process.
