                  YOUR USE OF THE APPS. TOTAL LIABILITY FOR ANY CLAIM SHALL NOT EXCEED THE AMOUNT YOU PAID IN THE 12 MONTHS PRECEDING THE
                  CLAIM.
                </p>
              </section>

