                <h2 id="terms-indemnity">9) Indemnification</h2>
                <p>
                  You agree to indemnify and hold harmless JHD and its licensors from any claims, losses, and expenses (including
                  reasonable attorneys’ fees) arising from your violation of these Terms or misuse of the apps.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-termination">
                <h2 id="terms-termination">10) Termination</h2>
                <p>
                  We may suspend or terminate access if you breach these Terms. You may uninstall or discontinue use at any time; this
                  does not entitle you to refunds beyond each platform’s policies.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-changes">
                <h2 id="terms-changes">11) Changes to These Terms</h2>
                <p>
                  We may update these Terms as the apps evolve. We’ll update the “Last Updated” date above and, when needed, announce
                  changes in-app. Continued use after updates means you accept the new Terms.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-governing-law">
                <h2 id="terms-governing-law">12) Governing Law</h2>
                <p>
                  These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Delaware, USA, without regard to its conflict of laws rules. Venue
                  for disputes shall be the state or federal courts located in Delaware, where permissible.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-app-store">
                <h2 id="terms-app-store">13) App Store Requirements</h2>
                <p>
                  If you downloaded the app from the Apple App Store or Google Play, you also agree to their terms. Neither Apple nor
